fixedRecordData.semantics:
The SOTDMA (Self-organized time-division multiple access communication state) communication state provides the following functions according to [ITU-R  M.1371-5]: 
- it contains information used by the slot allocation algorithm in the SOTDMA concept; 
- it also indicates the synchronization state.

The ITDMA communication state provides the following functions according to [ITU-R  M.1371-5]: 
- it contains information used by the slot allocation algorithm in the ITDMA concept; 
- it also indicates the synchronization state.
